PROUD TO SUPPORT SPECIAL OL YMPICS
We’ve been a proud supporter of the Special Olympics for multiple years, most notably in Kentucky, Texas, 
and Illinois. The Armadillo Classic Golf Scramble has donated more than $2.3 million to Special Olympics of 
Kentucky since 2000; and Tip-A-Cop Fundraisers have donated $1,746,602 to Special Olympics of Texas over 
the past 14 years.
